songs.title: No New Friends*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Verse]
-No new friends, nigga, are you stupid
No new friends, nigga, boy, how you lose me? (Why you lose me?)
Keep talkin' that shit, but are you doin' it? (But are you doin' it?)
No new friends, no new friends (No, no)
I can't trust a nigga, no, no-
